trans-unit.source: Exposes a generic <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> of designer glyphs associated with an activity designer.
trans-unit.target: Expõe um <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> genérico dos glifos de designer associados ao designer de atividade.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection> contains all designer glyphs that appear on the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner> class with which the collection is associated.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection> contém todos os glifos de designer que aparecem no <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner> classe à qual a coleção está associada.

trans-unit.source: You can access the contents of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection> through the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner.Glyphs%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Você pode acessar o conteúdo do <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection> por meio de <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner.Glyphs%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> class that is empty and has the default initial capacity.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> que está vazia e tem a capacidade inicial padrão.
Coleção genérica enumerável que contém objetos <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerGlyph" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> class that contains elements copied from the specified generic collection of <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerGlyph" />, and has sufficient capacity to accommodate the number of elements copied.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" />, que contém os elementos copiados da coleção genérica especificada do <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerGlyph" /> e tem capacidade suficiente para acomodar o número de elementos copiados.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> from which to copy collection elements.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> do qual copiar elementos de coleção.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> class that contains elements copied from the specified <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> and has sufficient capacity to accommodate the number of elements copied.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" />, que contém os elementos copiados do <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> especificado e tem capacidade suficiente para acomodar o número de elementos copiados.
